    "short_description": "Analyze SAP Plant Maintenance notifications for data quality, equipment reliability, and regulatory compliance using AI.",
    "long_description": "The PM Notification Analyzer leverages AI to transform SAP Plant Maintenance (PM/EAM) notification data into actionable insights. Built natively on SAP BTP with SAPUI5/Fiori, it integrates seamlessly with your existing SAP landscape.\n\nKey capabilities:\n- AI-powered notification text analysis with Google Gemini\n- ALCOA+ data quality scoring for FDA 21 CFR Part 11 compliance\n- Equipment reliability engineering (MTBF, MTTR, FMEA, availability)\n- Predictive maintenance indicators and failure probability scoring\n- Quality Management System (QMS) integration (Veeva Vault, MasterControl, SAP QM)\n- Multi-language support (English, German)\n- Comprehensive audit trail and change document tracking\n- GDPR-compliant data handling with self-service data export and erasure\n\nDesigned for regulated industries including pharmaceutical, chemical, food & beverage, and discrete manufacturing where maintenance data quality and compliance are critical.",
